Name: TypeOfPretestCollectionMode
Description: Specifies the type of data collection mode used (i.e. interview, self-completed form, observation). Supports the use of a controlled vocabulary.

Name: Description
Description: Description of mode of data collection for the pretest. Supports multiple language versions of the same content as well as optional formatting of the content.

Name: MethodOfDelivery
Description: Method of delivery for the pretest mode (i.e., mail, hand-delivery, etc.). Supports the use of a controlled vocabulary.

Name: IsPrimary
Description: A value of true indicates that this is the primary mode of data collection.

Name: IsAudioFormatAvailable
Description: A value of true indicates that an audio format of the question text is available.

Name: IsRecordedInterview
Description: A value of true indicates that the interview is recorded.
